Rainer Maria were a first class girl-fronted emo/power pop 3 piece, consisting of Caithlin De Marrais (vocals/bass), Kyle Fischer (vocals/guitar) and William Kuehn (Drums).

They disbanded in 2006 and are sorely missed.
